⍝ ZBus.Nats AOT smoke test
⍝ Validates: Init → Connect → Subscribe → Publish → Wait for Msg → Close
⍝ Requires nats-server running on localhost:4222

⎕IO ⎕ML←1
pass←1

dll←'D:\devel\Z-Format\src\ZBus.Nats\bin\Release\net10.0\win-x64\publish\ZBus.Nats.dll'

⍝ ── Define ⎕NA bindings ──────────────────────────────────────────────

'zbus_init'         ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_init <0T1 >Z'
'zbus_wait'         ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_wait& <0T1 I4 >Z >Z >Z'
'zbus_close'        ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_close <0T1'
'zbus_exists'       ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_exists <0T1'
'nats_connect'      ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_connect <0T1 <0T1'
'nats_pub'          ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_pub <0T1 <0T1 <Z'
'nats_sub'          ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_sub <0T1 <0T1 =Z'

⍝ ── Test 1: Init ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←'Test 1: Init'
(rc rootName)←zbus_init 'N1' 0
⎕←'  rc=',(⍕rc),' rootName=',rootName
:If rc≠0 ⋄ ⎕←'  FAIL' ⋄ pass←0 ⋄ :EndIf

⍝ ── Test 2: Connect ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←'Test 2: Connect'
rc←nats_connect 'N1' 'nats://localhost:4222'
⎕←'  connect rc=',⍕rc
:If rc≠0 ⋄ ⎕←'  FAIL' ⋄ pass←0 ⋄ :EndIf

⍝ Wait for Connected event
⎕←'  waiting for Connected event...'
(rc obj evt data)←zbus_wait 'N1' 5000 0 0 0
⎕←'  rc=',(⍕rc),' obj=',obj,' evt=',evt
:If evt≢'Connected' ⋄ ⎕←'  FAIL (expected Connected, got ',evt,')' ⋄ pass←0 ⋄ :EndIf

⍝ ── Test 3: Subscribe ────────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←'Test 3: Subscribe'
(rc subName)←nats_sub 'N1' 'prices' 'test.prices'
⎕←'  rc=',(⍕rc),' subName=',subName
:If rc≠0 ⋄ ⎕←'  FAIL' ⋄ pass←0 ⋄ :EndIf

⍝ ── Test 4: Publish + receive ────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←'Test 4: Publish and receive'
rc←nats_pub 'N1' 'test.prices' 'hello NATS'
⎕←'  pub rc=',⍕rc
:If rc≠0 ⋄ ⎕←'  FAIL (publish)' ⋄ pass←0 ⋄ :EndIf

⍝ Wait for Msg event
(rc obj evt data)←zbus_wait 'N1' 5000 0 0 0
⎕←'  rc=',(⍕rc),' obj=',obj,' evt=',evt
:If evt≢'Msg'
    ⎕←'  FAIL (expected Msg, got ',evt,')'
    pass←0
:Else
    ⎕←'  payload subject: ',1⊃data
    ⎕←'  SUCCESS — message received!'
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test 5: Close ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←'Test 5: Close root'
rc←zbus_close ⊂'N1'
⎕←'  close rc=',⍕rc
:If rc≠0 ⋄ ⎕←'  FAIL' ⋄ pass←0 ⋄ :EndIf

⎕←''
:If pass
    ⎕←'═══ ALL SMOKE TESTS PASSED ═══'
:Else
    ⎕←'*** SOME TESTS FAILED ***'
:EndIf
